Revision history for Perl extension Math::ES.

0.01  Mon Mar 10 22:10:25 2003
 
Initial version

--------------------------------------------------------------------
0.02  

First version to export, basic functions seem to work properly.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
0.03

Added POD, lots of stuff

--------------------------------------------------------------------
0.04

Added basic retrieval methods, included debug and log output.
Added a validation routine.
Extended POD.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
0.05

Added LICENSE, cleaned Makefile.PL.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
0.06

Minor changes
--------------------------------------------------------------------

--------------------------------------------------------------------
0.07

Extended documentation a bit.

Included minimum and maximum value arrays for the gene_deviations, 
because in production use it often occured that single deviation 
values climbed up to gigantical heights, that then caused problems 
in finding new genes within the given boundaries... 
--------------------------------------------------------------------

--------------------------------------------------------------------
0.08

Fixed a bug in the elitism feature.
Extended README.txt.
